<br>
I'm not saying Indies should or shouldn't be on the list.  I'm just saying your arguement for being there doesn't hold water.  I personally don't think Indies are the problem.  There are not that many Indies on the lists.  The problem is the numerous small guilds on the lists that can barely field 12 people in a 36-42 person raid. When littleguildA has Vox and invites LittleguildB then LittleguildB has Vox they invite LittleguildA that is the problem.  The same 36 people are taking up two spots in the rotation when they should be sharing one.<br>
